{"tid":1469461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家討論機場嘅同時 都幫手宣傳下818","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:51:12.000Z","uid":43009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6db31c6df05ab240cf38693cbcd728a5075d46d0","tid":1469461,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"我地由812開始入機場嘅初心係警察還眼<br />\n我相信盲眼少女都唔想見到我地內鬨<br />\n請大家毋忘811警察暴動<br />\n宣傳818遊行<br />\n繼續俾最大壓力政府<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w32jDrT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw32jDrT.jpg&h=b2aefb2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83bbfd72064b5c2568e5952d55360db22b2855e1","tid":1469461,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:57:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ffdcf35a1d07b42dc832ffc553b73180790fa4","tid":1469461